Cell["\<\
This is the pattern we saw earlier for replacing a part of an expression with \
an evaluated expression:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.685311620629414*^9, {3.6853201104764338`*^9, 3.6853201603240757`*^9}, {
